messages.content: Emperor has some toys and a lot of snacks in here
"Yeah I pick up a lot of stuff I can find!" this includes a book of Pokemon cards
"I dunno what these pokemon critters are but they look cool!"
Vega placed Star on his head "This is Star!!!!"
She shook her head "Hss a rat!!!!"
"Oh, I think I've only seen a few of those in prison."
Emperor offers her a piece of candy
"I have games in here too!" He gets out Monopoly, Scrabble and Battleship
"Do you wanna play one of these?"
"Let's start with scrabble. that's the easiest." He taught her how to play Scrabble as simply as possible and then gave both sides their letters
He realized he only had non-vowels on his side
She thinks for a bit before just putting letters down. Shes....not good at spelling yet...
//what specific letters did she place down
"hmmm." Emperor placed an m in front of the I and 2 S's after it. "Miss."
Shes....just placing ramdom letters down without a care. She doesn't get how to play
She shook her head "Mamas still teaching mr how to spell!!"
"I can help!" he grabs a picture book and points to a picture of a fish. "This is a fish. Can you spell that?"
She stared "Fish....F....I...H?????" She tilted her bead
"S and H make a 'sh' sound when put together."
he points at a whale. "Can you spell whale?"
he points to a cow. "This one is easy. Cow!"
She....starts to sing the baby shark song...
Emperor has never heard this song before and is confusion
Shes doing the little dance that goes with it
"I know a dance." Emp proceeded to do the macarena
Emperor hugged back. He was only ever hugged a few times in his life
She smiled and tried to climb him...
Emperor wasn't that much taller so he was kinda startled
